.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Music-Genre: rock, jazz, indie, blues
1. Music-Genre:blues is between Hobby:reading and Music-Genre:jazz##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is on the right of Music-Genre:rock##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Music-Genre:rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | blues   | rock | indie       |

