2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and Pet:lizard##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Pet:turtle##1
5. Pet:lizard == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet          | chinchilla    | ferret | lizard   | turtle  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

